message.content: The paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "Information Retrieval" (cs.IR) as it integrates the Anserini information retrieval toolkit with BERT for question answering. Other likely sub-categories could include "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI), "Computation and Language" (cs.CL), "Machine Learning" (cs.LG), and "Natural Language Processing" (cs.NE).
